(3042, 1, '2018-12-07 15:39:39', '2018-12-07 15:39:39', '[vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1534280819684{margin-top: 90px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\" el_class=\"page-sidebar\"][vc_column el_class=\"page-sidebar\"][vc_wp_custommenu title=\"About Us\" nav_menu=\"12\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"content-heading\" css=\".vc_custom_1534280639628{margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column][pt_single_image image=\"2868\" img_size=\"1500x450\" image_align=\"text-center\" onclick=\"\" css_animation=\"\" pt_hidden_viewport=\"\" caption=\"\" css_delay=\"\" el_class=\"\"][pt_text color=\"\" css_animation=\"\" pt_hidden_viewport=\"\" css_delay=\"\" el_class=\"\" css=\"\"]\r\n<h2>About Us</h2>\r\n[/pt_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1534519413172{margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column][vc_tta_tabs][vc_tta_section title=\"Vision\" tab_id=\"vision\"][pt_text color=\"\" css_animation=\"\" pt_hidden_viewport=\"\" css_delay=\"\" el_class=\"\" css=\"\"]Our vision is for our business to be a fully pan-Nigeria sales / marketing world class organization and operating international standard best practices, processes &amp; procedures.[/pt_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Mission\" tab_id=\"mission\"][pt_text color=\"\" css_animation=\"\" pt_hidden_viewport=\"\" css_delay=\"\" el_class=\"\" css=\"\"]Our Mission is to achieve excellence in our products and services, sustained by the continuous investment in our people, processes and technologies.[/pt_text][/vc_tta_section][vc_tta_section title=\"Values\" tab_id=\"values\"][pt_text color=\"\" css_animation=\"\" pt_hidden_viewport=\"\" css_delay=\"\" el_class=\"\" css=\"\"]<strong>HERITAGE:</strong>\r\n\r\nWe’ve stood the test of time; we are the one referred to as the successful company with a rich heritage and a great track record of growth and performance.\r\n\r\n<strong><u>CORE VALUES;</u></strong>\r\n\r\n<strong> </strong>Our central belief is that “we will keep our promises and deliver our commitments”.\r\n\r\n<strong>A</strong>CCOUNTABIITY:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>We are all here to do a job. That job and its responsibilities come first above all else</li>\r\n 	<li>In not doing our jobs we let ourselves down, we let our colleagues down, we let our                     business down</li>\r\n 	<li>So we focus our energy on doing the right thing, the right way, at the right time. Always!!</li>\r\n</ul>\r\nThere lies the path to success.\r\n\r\n<strong>T</strong>OGETHERNESS:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>We recognize that every individual matter.</li>\r\n 	<li>What we do matters.</li>\r\n 	<li>How we do it matters.</li>\r\n 	<li>When we do it matters.</li>\r\n 	<li>We can make an impact.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>O</strong>NENESS:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>The Company and its employees share a deep bond. Our pact is simple;</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>N</strong>ETWORKING:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>We work towards a common goal through cooperation and teamwork; thus we build long lasting relationship through shared interest</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<strong>E</strong>NERGY:\r\n<ul>\r\n 	<li>We approach each day with a passion and persistence to exceed expectations</li>\r\n 	<li>We demonstrate high energy to back check, identify and solve challenges that we come across daily.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n[/pt_text][/vc_tta_section][/vc_tta_tabs][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'About Us', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '43-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-07 15:39:39', '2018-12-07 15:39:39', '', 43, 'http://grandoak.ga/43-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0);
