(3048, 1, '2018-12-07 15:59:01', '2018-12-07 15:59:01', '[vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1534280819684{margin-top: 90px !important;margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\" el_class=\"page-sidebar\"][vc_column el_class=\"page-sidebar\"][vc_wp_custommenu title=\"Careers\" nav_menu=\"15\"][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row el_class=\"content-heading\" css=\".vc_custom_1534280639628{margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column][pt_single_image image=\"3040\" img_size=\"1500x450\" image_align=\"text-center\" onclick=\"\" css_animation=\"\" pt_hidden_viewport=\"\" caption=\"\" css_delay=\"\" el_class=\"\"][pt_text color=\"\" css_animation=\"\" pt_hidden_viewport=\"\" css_delay=\"\" el_class=\"\" css=\"\"]\r\n<h2>Life at GOL</h2>\r\n[/pt_text][/vc_column][/vc_row][vc_row css=\".vc_custom_1534519413172{margin-bottom: 50px !important;}\"][vc_column][pt_text color=\"\" css_animation=\"\" pt_hidden_viewport=\"\" css_delay=\"\" el_class=\"\" css=\"\"]GOL gives you a unique experience with employees from diverse background and culture. Every day at GOL is a learning and fun experience.\r\n\r\n<strong>MEET OUR PEOPLE   </strong>\r\n\r\n<strong>Our beliefs </strong>\r\n\r\nHR Pulse\r\n\r\nWe believe that our people are the greatest asset in the organization; therefore we adopt the best-practice in our hiring process to ensure we not only hire the right people, we hire people who believe in our values, enjoy &amp; want to grow with the company\r\n\r\nWe believe that there is a ripple effect by taking care of your employees which will lead to success of the business, therefore we ensure we provide conducive working environment &amp; also ensure that our employee engagement activities are impactful\r\n\r\nWe believe in recognizing success, this can be seen in the <strong><em>“Sales Incentive Scheme” “Grand Master Awards\" </em></strong>and other schemes that awards achievement &amp; success.\r\n\r\nWe believe in developing our people through on-the –job training, regional training &amp; overseas trainings\r\n\r\nWe believe our employees are business partners, so we often conduct survey to know the views of our employees in order to use the valuable information to make strategic decisions.\r\n\r\n<strong><em>Employee Engagement Initiatives:</em></strong>\r\n\r\nWe have created a staff communication session at the Head Office on a monthly basis and on a quarterly basis in the area offices. The motive behind organizing such activities in unit is to inculcate a sense of responsibility among the general workers towards the society, nation and working place out of their day to day usual activities/affairs.[/pt_text][/vc_column][/vc_row]', 'Life at GOL', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '2702-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-12-07 15:59:01', '2018-12-07 15:59:01', '', 2702, 'http://grandoak.ga/2702-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
